723349f-a.title: Manhattan: South Street - Gouverneur Slip
723349f-a.folder: South Street & Gouverneur Slip, Manhattan, NY

723350f-b.title: Manhattan: South Street - Gouverneur Slip
723350f-b.text:
South Street, east from Gouverneur Slip, showing a
small park in the foreground and industrial build-
ings beyond. These will be removed to provide for
the marginal East River Drive. Gouverneur Hospital
at the left, facing on Front Street, will then be
open to view.
1: March 23, 1937
2: Sept. 18, 1939
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
